com.yworks.yfiles.algorithms

Interface IDataProvider

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDataMap, IEdgeMap, INodeMap
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataMapAdapter, DataProviderAdapter, DataProviderAdapter

    public interface IDataProvider
    A general interface for data provision.

    A data provider grants access to data associated with one or more data holders. It constitutes a read-only view on particular data.
